---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import staffImage1 from '@images/stock/ourEmployees.png'
import staffImage2 from '@images/stock/ourEmployees2.png'
import staffImage3 from '@images/stock/ourEmployees3.png'

const t1 =
  'We invest considerable time and expense in our most important asset, our security personnel. Our pre-employment process is extensive. Verification of state issued permits, and a thorough background check with criminal and civil index checks as well as interviews with former employers are performed. Upon passing our stringent screening process, new staff members are required to undergo advanced training in all areas related to, or specific to, their assigned duties to ensure smooth communications and client satisfaction. Additional training is provided by legal experts and Law Enforcement Trainers in the field of civil and criminal laws.'

const t2 =
  'Our entire employment process assists us in selecting qualified individuals who will ultimately provide the best security services available.'

const t3 =
  'Our employees are continually monitored, updated and trained in new laws and regulations. We believe customer service and satisfaction results from personnel that are professional and skilled in maintaining authority in the field while always exercising tact and diplomacy.'
---

{/* White Section - Mission Statement*/}
<section class="bg-white px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 md:py-16 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md lg:max-w-screen-xl">
    <div class="flex w-full justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-900">OUR EMPLOYEES</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 place-content-center my-8">
      <div class="m-auto">
        <Image
          src={staffImage1}
          alt='Our Employees'
          class="h-auto rounded-3xl object-cover object-center shadow-xl"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="m-auto">
        <Image
          src={staffImage2}
          alt='Our Employees'
          class="h-auto rounded-3xl object-cover object-center shadow-xl"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="m-auto">
        <Image
          src={staffImage3}
          alt='Our Employees'
          class="h-auto rounded-3xl object-cover object-center shadow-xl"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    {/* Project description */}
    <div class="mx-auto mt-6 flex w-full flex-wrap">
      <div class="mx-auto w-full">
        <p
          class="mb-6 text-2xl font-normal tracking-tight text-dark-900 lg:leading-tight"
        >
          {t1}
        </p>
        <p
          class="mb-6 text-2xl font-normal tracking-tight text-dark-900 lg:leading-tight"
        >
          {t2}
        </p>
        <p
          class="mb-6 text-2xl font-normal tracking-tight text-dark-900 lg:leading-tight"
        >
          {t3}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
